-featured\">\n <div class=\"blog-featured__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/medical-office-service.jpg\" alt=\"Professional medical office sanitation services\" loading=\"eager\" fetchpriority=\"high\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-featured__content\">\n <span class=\"blog-featured__category\">Infection Control</span>\n <h2 class=\"blog-featured__title\">\n <a href=\"/blog/infection-control-best-practices-medical-offices\">Infection Control Best Practices for Medical Offices</a>\n</h2>\n <p class=\"blog-featured__excerpt\">Comprehensive guide to CDC-aligned infection control protocols, EPA-registered disinfectants, and high-touch surface sanitation for Massachusetts medical offices.</p>\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">\n <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M19 3h-1V1h-2v2H8V1H6v2H5c-1.11 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L3 19c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H5V8h14v11zM9 10H7v2h2v-2zm4 0h-2v2h2v-2zm4 0h-2v2h2v-2z\"/></svg>\n February 20, 2026\n</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">\n <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z\"/></svg>\n 10 min read\n</span>\n</div>\n <a href=\"/blog/infection-control-best-practices-medical-offices\" class=\"blog-card__link\">\n Read Full Article\n <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg>\n</a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Section Title -->\n <div class=\"section__header\">\n <h2 class=\"section__title\">Latest Articles</h2>\n <p class=\"section__description\">Expert healthcare guides for Massachusetts medical facilities</p>\n</div>\n\n <!-- Blog Grid -->\n <div class=\"blog-grid\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n <!-- Medical Offices Post 1 - Featured -->\n <article class=\"blog-card blog-card--featured\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/medical-office-service.jpg\" alt=\"Complete surface sanitation for medical offices\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Medical Offices</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Feb 20, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">10 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/infection-control-best-practices-medical-offices\">Complete Surface Sanitation Guide for Medical Offices</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">A thorough look at surface sanitation and disinfection for medical office environments, covering floor care, high-touch area attention, restroom sanitation, and environmental cleaning to keep your practice safe and compliant.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/infection-control-best-practices-medical-offices\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Medical Offices Post 2 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/medical-office-highttouch.jpg\" alt=\"High-touch area disinfection in medical offices\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Medical Offices</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Feb 15, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">9 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/choosing-healthcare-cleaning-service-massachusetts\">High-Touch Area Disinfection: Protecting Your Medical Office Patients</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">Doorknobs, exam tables, waiting room chairs, and check-in counters are among the most critical high-touch surfaces in medical offices. Learn how targeted disinfection protocols and routine environmental cleaning reduce infection risk and safeguard patient health.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/choosing-healthcare-cleaning-service-massachusetts\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Specialty Clinics Post 3 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/specialty-clinic.webp\" alt=\"Specialty clinic sanitation for cardiology practices\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Specialty Clinics</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Feb 10, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">8 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/cdc-compliance-environmental-sanitation-clinics\">Specialty Clinic Sanitation: What Cardiology Practices Need to Know</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">Professional sanitation for specialty clinics like cardiology practices demands careful attention to clinical workflow and patient safety environments. Discover the protocols that keep diagnostic equipment areas, procedure rooms, and patient spaces thoroughly sanitized.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/cdc-compliance-environmental-sanitation-clinics\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Specialty Clinics Post 4 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/clinic-workflow.jpg\" alt=\"Maintaining patient safety in specialty clinic environments\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Specialty Clinics</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Feb 5, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">9 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/infection-prevention-assisted-living-facilities\">Maintaining Patient Safety Through Clinical Workflow-Aligned Sanitation</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">Specialty clinics operate on tight schedules with sensitive equipment and vulnerable patients. Learn how professional sanitation services integrate seamlessly with clinical workflows, ensuring every treatment area, waiting room, and staff zone meets the highest safety standards.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/infection-prevention-assisted-living-facilities\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Ambulatory & Outpatient Facilities Post 5 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/ambulatory-care.jpg\" alt=\"Sanitation support for ambulatory care centers\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Ambulatory & Outpatient Facilities</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Jan 30, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">8 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/scheduled-sanitation-program-healthcare-facilities\">Structured Sanitation Support for Ambulatory Care Centers</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">Ambulatory care centers and outpatient facilities require sanitation programs designed around clinical schedules and patient flow. Explore how structured sanitation support keeps these fast-paced environments clean, compliant, and ready for every patient visit.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/scheduled-sanitation-program-healthcare-facilities\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Ambulatory & Outpatient Facilities Post 6 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/outpatient-flow.jpg\" alt=\"Patient flow and sanitation in outpatient facilities\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Ambulatory & Outpatient Facilities</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Jan 20, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">8 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/hipaa-compliant-cleaning-medical-offices\">How Patient Flow Impacts Sanitation in Outpatient Facilities</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">Outpatient facilities see high volumes of patients throughout the day, making sanitation timing critical. Learn how to align cleaning schedules with patient flow patterns to minimize disruption while maintaining a consistently safe and hygienic clinical environment.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/hipaa-compliant-cleaning-medical-offices\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Rehabilitation & Nursing Facilities Post 7 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/rehab-center.jpg\" alt=\"Sanitation services for rehabilitation centers\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Rehabilitation & Nursing Facilities</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Jan 12, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">7 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/dental-office-sterilization-environmental-services\">Dependable Sanitation for Rehabilitation Centers: Safety Meets Comfort</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">Rehabilitation centers serve patients in recovery who need clean, safe surroundings to heal. Dependable sanitation services prioritize safety, professionalism, and resident comfort, ensuring therapy areas, common spaces, and patient rooms are thoroughly maintained.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/dental-office-sterilization-environmental-services\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Rehabilitation & Nursing Facilities Post 8 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/nursing-facility.jpg\" alt=\"Nursing facility sanitation and resident well-being\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Rehabilitation & Nursing Facilities</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Jan 5, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">9 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/epa-registered-disinfectants-healthcare-guide\">Nursing Facility Sanitation: Prioritizing Resident Well-Being Every Day</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">In nursing facilities, sanitation directly impacts resident health and quality of life. From dining areas to individual rooms, professional environmental cleaning maintains the dignified, hygienic living spaces that residents and their families expect and deserve.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/epa-registered-disinfectants-healthcare-guide\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Healthcare Admin Offices Post 9 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/admin-office.jpg\" alt=\"Environmental cleaning for healthcare administrative offices\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Healthcare Admin Offices</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Dec 28, 2025</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">8 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/healthcare-cleaning-staff-training-certification\">Professional Environmental Cleaning for Healthcare Admin Spaces</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">Healthcare administrative offices are the operational backbone of clinical organizations. Professional environmental cleaning keeps these spaces organized, hygienic, and welcoming, supporting the staff who manage patient records, billing, and day-to-day clinical operations.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/healthcare-cleaning-staff-training-certification\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- Healthcare Admin Offices Post 10 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/admin-operations.jpg\" alt=\"Clean healthcare admin offices supporting clinical operations\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">Healthcare Admin Offices</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Dec 20, 2025</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">10 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/operating-room-terminal-cleaning-protocols\">Why Clean Admin Offices Are Essential to Clinical Operations</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">A clean healthcare administrative environment does more than look professional -- it supports clinical operations by reducing sick days, improving staff morale, and maintaining the organized workspaces needed for accurate record-keeping and efficient healthcare management.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/operating-room-terminal-cleaning-protocols\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <!-- NEW POSTS April 2026 -->\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/infection-control.jpg\" alt=\"OSHA cleaning requirements for medical offices\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__category\">OSHA Compliance</span>\n</div>\n <div class=\"blog-card__body\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__meta\">\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">Apr 1, 2026</span>\n <span class=\"blog-card__meta-item\">12 min</span>\n</div>\n <h3 class=\"blog-card__title\"><a href=\"/blog/osha-cleaning-requirements-medical-offices-2026\">OSHA Cleaning Requirements for Medical Offices in 2026</a></h3>\n <p class=\"blog-card__excerpt\">Complete guide to OSHA environmental cleaning requirements including bloodborne pathogen standards, PPE protocols, and compliance documentation for Massachusetts medical offices.</p>\n <a href=\"/blog/osha-cleaning-requirements-medical-offices-2026\" class=\"blog-card__link\">Read More <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/></svg></a>\n</div>\n </article>\n\n <article class=\"blog-card\">\n <div class=\"blog-card__image\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/blog/infection-control.jpg\" alt=\"Terminal cleaning vs concurrent cleaning in healthcare\" loading=\"la